4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with in-demand skills in technologies such as JavaScript and Python. The bootcamp lasts for 18 weeks, divided into 16 weeks of instruction and 2 weeks for project work, with classes held thrice a week in small groups (1 instructor for every 7 students). Students will engage in hands-on projects and will not require prior coding experience. Upon completion, participants will receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. Instruction is available in English and Spanish. For further details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop